{"word":"πολύκλυστος","slug":"πολύκλυστος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πολύκλυστος</b></el> <el>(πολύ-κλυστος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κλύζω'><el>κλύζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>much-dashing</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b> <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <i>washed by many a wave</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}